    SELECT TOP(1) [h].[Id]
    FROM [Habits] AS [h]
    WHERE [h].[Id] = @__habitId_0
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [DayResults] AS [d] ON [t].[Id] = [d].[HabitId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]
